This paper focuses on search systems and information retrieval, which falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of algorithms and models for natural language processing, which could fall under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques, which could fall under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the task of query expansion, which could involve deep learning techniques, falling under Deep Learning (cs.DL).
